text: Mochammad Al Amin Syukur Fisabillah (born 10 May 1995 in Bontang) is an Indonesian professional footballer who plays as a centre-back for Liga 2 club Kalteng Putra. ==Career== ===Kalteng Putra=== He was signed for Kalteng Putra to played in Liga 2 on 2020 season. ==References== == External links == * Mochamad Sabillah at Soccerway * Mochamad Sabillah at Liga Indonesia Category:1995 births Category:Badak Lampung F.C. players Category:Indonesian footballers Category:Persijap Jepara players Category:PSIM Yogyakarta players Category:Liga 2 (Indonesia) players Category:Liga 1 (Indonesia) players Category:Persibat Batang players Category:Association football defenders Category:Persib Bandung players Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Malang
title: Moch Al Amin Syukur Fisabillah
